posts.subject: Has anyone played Dragon Quest XI S on Switch
posts.body:
Anyone here played DQXI? I ignored it when I saw it was releasing on PS4, and after playing the 10 hour Switch demo recently, realised I made a good decision. The symphonic soundtrack is what ultimately sold me on a purchase. Definitely enjoyed the experience of a good turn based 3D JRPG. 
I'm planning on purchasing it along with a few other Switch titles. Has anyone here played it or considered playing it?
